For Tri-Semester System, there are three semesters in each academic year:


1. Spring semester begins from 2nd  week of January and continues for four months;

2. Summer semester begins from 2nd week of May and continues for four months;

3. Fall Semester begins from 2nd week of September and continues for four months.

For Bi-Semester System, there are two semesters in each academic year:


1. Spring semester begins from January  and continues for Six months;

2. Fall Semester begins from July and continues for Six months.
